@Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7001
@BearerToken = your-jwt-token-here

# Swagger UI is available at: {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/swagger
# Update the host address above based on your launchSettings.json configuration

### Health Check
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/health
Accept: application/json

### Get Current User (requires authentication)
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Validate Token
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/validate
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Get User Companies
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/companies
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Search Employees
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/employees/search?searchTerm=john
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Get Employee by Number
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/employees/EMP001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Get Employees by Company
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/employees/company/001?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Get Layoff Requests
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/layoffrequests?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

### Get Layoff Request by ID
GET {{Mathy.ELM.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/layoffrequests/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###
